{
  "id": "adv_event_2111_01_05",
  "title": "貴方の娘より",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "……お父さん……？\nえっ？　お父さん来てる……なんで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Father?\nEh? Father’s here? Why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.26
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "お父様は、私がちゃんと席にご案内しましたわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve guided him to his seat!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3,
      "endTime": 14.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "緊急の手術が入って遅れてしまったそうなのですが……\nそうならそうと、連絡してくださればいいのに、もう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apparently there was an urgent surgery‚ so he ran late…\nHe could have called to say so! *sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.7,
      "endTime": 24.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "（……そういえば、お父さんは、言い訳が嫌いだった）\n（言葉じゃなくて、行動で示せって、よく言ってた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Reminds me‚ father hates excuses.)\n(He often said “show people your actions‚ not words.”)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1333333333,
      "endTime": 36.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "（……お父さん、少し遅れちゃったけど）\n（言い訳しないで、頑張って来てくれたんだね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…My father ran a little late‚)\n(but he didn’t make excuses‚ he came.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1333333333,
      "endTime": 43.800000000033336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "（じゃあ、私もこのステージで示してみせるよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I’m going to show him with this performance.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2333333333,
      "endTime": 47.96666666663333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "（アイドルが、人生を懸ける価値がある仕事だって）\n（私が、本気の本気なんだって……！！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I’ll show him that being an idol is a job worth staking your life on.)\n(I’ll show him that I’m seriously determined!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1666666667,
      "endTime": 55.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9033.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、よかったね！\nお父さんに観てもらえるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan‚ that’s great!\nYour father is watching you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0333333333,
      "endTime": 61.70000000003333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "うん、絶対、最高のステージにしてみせる\nだから芽衣、私に力を貸して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll make it absolutely the best show!\nThat’s why I need your help‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9,
      "endTime": 69.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだよ！　怜ちゃんと芽衣の両親に\n娘の晴れ姿を目に焼き付けてもらおうね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! Let’s make their daughter’s hour of triumph\ninto a memorable image for our parents.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5,
      "endTime": 77.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "うん、行くよ！　芽衣！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ let’s go Mei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9,
      "endTime": 80.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3099.9999999999945
        }
