    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 92.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "どうですか？　お父様\n怜さんのパフォーマンス",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So what did you think of\nRei-san’s performance‚ Mr. Ichinose?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0666666667,
      "endTime": 97.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-reidad001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、君は成宮さんところの……また来てくれたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you’re Narumiya-san… You came again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5,
      "endTime": 108.17356014251709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さっきは席の案内をありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for showing us to our seats earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9,
      "endTime": 108.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "怜さんは、歌とダンスをあそこまで磨き上げるのに\n時間をかけて、ハードな練習を積んできました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-san spent a lot of time and hard practice\nto get her singing and dancing so good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6666666667,
      "endTime": 116.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "怜さんの……アイドルの仕事は決していいかげんな\n気持ちで出来るような簡単なものではありませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-san’s job… An idol’s job is certainly not a simple thing\nanyone can do with a half-hearted attitude.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.6666666667,
      "endTime": 124.76666666663333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-reidad002.m4a",
      "text": "……私は、芸能のたぐいには詳しくありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know much about show business‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.9333333333,
      "endTime": 132.75802701310957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だから、良し悪しなんてものは分からないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I can’t tell what’s good and what’s bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.3666666667,
      "endTime": 133.10000000003333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、お父様――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Mr. Ichinose…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3,
      "endTime": 135.10000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_05-reidad003.m4a",
      "text": "だが、これだけの人が集まり、熱狂している",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if so many people are gathered here and getting excited‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3,
      "endTime": 144.46702938079835,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1933.3333332999985
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "怜は自分の仕事を全うしているんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei must be doing her job well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.6,
      "endTime": 144.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
